    <content>&lt;P&gt;You probably installed ABAP trial which contains only the basis components of ABAP-based software.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;MARA and EKPO tables are part of SAP ERP or S/4HANA, which is made of the basis components + the ERP components. You are probably interested by such software with demonstration data, so you should install either IDES (you can find the different versions available to you in the SAP Support portal) or via appliance (&lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/notes/2041140/E" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;2041140 - Order an SAP S/4HANA fully-activated appliance for on-premise deployment - SAP for Me&lt;/A&gt; "Request the delivery of the appliance by creating a support ticket on the component XX-SER-SWFL-SHIP...")&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Also see this answer in 2022:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/availability-sap-s-4hana-ides/qaq-p/12533877" target="_blank"&gt;Availability SAP S/4HANA IDES - SAP Community&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
